usca restaurar la monarqu\u00eda|website=EL DEBATE|language=es-ES|access-date=2020-04-12}}</ref>\n|-\n|9\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |{{flaglist|Hawaii}}\n|355,123\n|25%\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.denverpost.com/2008/06/19/native-hawaiians-seek-to-restore-monarchy/|title=Native Hawaiians seek to restore monarchy|last=Press|first=The Associated|date=2008-06-19|website=The Denver Post|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-12}}</ref>\n|-\n|10\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |{{flaglist|Austria}}\n|1,754,600\n|20%\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |<ref>{{cite news |title=A century after Austrian-Hungarian Empire's fall, some nostalgic for monarchy |url=https://www.efe.com/efe/english/patrocinada/a-century-after-austrian-hungarian-empire-s-fall-some-nostalgic-for-monarchy/50000268-3809622# |accessdate=3 December 2018 |work=EFE |language=en}}</ref>\n|-\n|11\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |{{flaglist|Germany}}\n|15,646,310\n|19%\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |<ref>{{cite news |title=Restored monarchy gains young Germans' support |url=https://www.thelocal.de/20130425/49371 |accessdate=3 December 2018 |work=The Local |date=25 April 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n|12\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |{{flaglist|France}}\n|11,053,890\n|17%\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |<ref>{{cite web |url=https://staticswww.bva-group.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/fichier_bva_pour_lalliance_royale_-_les_francais_et_la_monarchiefe87e.pdf |publisher=BVA |accessdate=3 December 2018|title=BVA Group - Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 d'\u00e9tudes et conseil }}</ref>\n|-\n|13\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |{{flaglist|Italy}}\n|6,500,000\n|15%\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |<ref>{{cite news |title=Emanule Filiberto: \"Politici? Sono dei parac***\"\". Occhio, il Savoia vuole fare il re |url=https://www.liberoquotidiano.it/news/personaggi/13359754/emanuele-filiberto-savoia-partito-monarchico-15-per-cento-sondaggio-piepoli.html |accessdate=3 December 2018 |language=it}}</ref>\n|-\n|14\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |{{flaglist|Portugal}}\n|1,546,435\n|15%\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |<ref>{{cite news |last1=Almeida |first1=Henrique |title=Portugal royal says monarchy still tops republic |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-portugal-king/portugal-royal-says-monarchy-still-tops-republic-idUSL0917595020070709 |accessdate=3 December 2018 |work=Reuters}}</ref>\n|-\n|15\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |{{flaglist|Greece}}\n|1,342,046\n|14%\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |<ref>{{cite news |title=\u03a4\u03bf \u0392\u0397\u039c\u0391 onLine - \u03a0\u039f\u039b\u0399\u03a4\u0399\u039a\u0391 |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070425203217/http://tovima.dolnet.gr/print_article.php?e=B&f=15044&m=A04&aa=1 |accessdate=3 December 2018 |date=25 April 2007 |language=greek}}</ref>\n|-\n|16\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |{{flaglist|Czech Republic}}\n|1,379,423\n|13%\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |<ref>{{cite news |title=Pr\u016fzkum ke 100 rok\u016fm od vzniku \u010ceskoslovenska: kdyby se monarchie nerozpadla, m\u011bli bychom se l\u00e9pe nebo stejn\u011b |url=https://www.irozhlas.cz/zpravy-domov/ceskoslovensko-28-rijen-1918-100-let-prvni-republika_1810031330_ako |accessdate=3 December 2018 |work=iROZHLAS |language=cs}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==Monarchists==\n{{Dynamic list|date=April 2019}}\n\n===American===\n{{see also|Loyalist (American Revolution)}}\n* [[Charles A. Coulombe]] (born 1960)<ref>{{cite book|title=Star-Spangled Crown: A Simple Guide to the American Monarchy|publisher=Tumblar House|year=2016|isbn=978-1-9443-3905-0|last=Coulombe|first=Charles A.}}</ref>\n\n===Australian===\n{{see also|Australian Monarchist League|Australians for Constitutional Monarchy}}\n* [[Joan Sutherland]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.abc.net.au/pm/content/2005/s1539160.htm|title=Sounds of Summer: Dame Joan Sutherland|publisher=Australian Broadcasting Corporation|date=2 January 2006|accessdate=18 April 2019|work=PM}}</ref> (1926\u20132010)\n* [[Tony Abbott]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/10293028/Ten-things-you-didnt-know-about-Tony-Abbott.html|last=Pearlman|first=Johnathan|title=Ten things you didn't know about Tony Abbott|work=telegraph.co.uk|publisher=Telegraph Media Group Limited|date=7 September 2013|accessdate=19 Nov 2013}}</ref><ref name=AbMir>{{cite book|title=Abbott's Gambit: The 2013 Australian Federal Election|last1=Johnson|first1=Carol|last2=Wanna|first2=John|last3=Lee|first3=Hsu-Ann|publisher=ANU Press|year=2015|isbn=978-1-9250-2209-4|page=281}}</ref> (born 1957)\n* [[Sophie Mirabella]]<ref name=AbMir/> (born 1968)\n*[[Scott Morrison]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.smh.com.au/world/europe/australia-s-position-on-a-republic-untenable-queen-elizabeth-ii-believes-20181017-p50a2x.html|title=Australia's position on a republic untenable: Queen 'believes'|last=Bourke|first=Latika|date=2018-10-17|website=The Sydney Morning Herald|language=en|access-date=2019-08-31}}</ref> (born 1968)\n\n===Austrian===\n* [[Georg von Trapp]]<ref>{{cite book|title=The Last Empress: The Life and Times of Zita of Austria-Hungary, 1892-1989|page=289|first=Brook-Shepherd|last=Gordon|year=1991|publisher=HarperCollins|isbn=0-0021-5861-2}}</ref> (1880\u20131947)\n* [[Joseph Roth]]<ref>{{cite book|title=Understanding Joseph Roth|last=Rosenfeld|first=Sidney|page=55|year=2001|publisher=University of South Carolina Press|isbn=1-5700-3398-6}}</ref> (1894\u20131939)\n* [[Erik von Kuehnelt-Leddihn]]<ref>{{cite journal|last1=von Kuehnelt-Leddihn|first=Erik|year=2001|title=Monarchy and War|journal=Journal of Libertarian Studies|volume=15|issue=1|pages=1\u201341|access-date=18 April 2019|url=https://mises.org/library/monarchy-and-war-0}}</ref> (1909\u20131999)\n* [[Ernst Fuchs (artist)|Ernst Fuchs]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://kurier.at/kultur/ernst-fuchs-posthum-als-monarchist-geoutet/280.754.340|title=Ernst Fuchs posthum als Monarchist geoutet|language=German|work=Kurier.at|publisher=Funke Mediengruppe|date=16 August 2017|accessdate=18 April 2019}}</ref> (1930\u20132015)\n* [[Alexander Tschugguel]] (b. 1993)\n\n===Brazilian===\n{{main|Monarchism in Brazil}}\n{{col div}}\n* [[Jos\u00e9 Bonif\u00e1cio de Andrada|Jos\u00e9 Bonif\u00e1cio]] (1763\u20131838)\n* [[Maria Quit\u00e9ria]] (1792\u20131853)\n* [[F\u00e9lix Taunay, Baron of Taunay|Baron of Taunay]] (1795\u20131881)\n* [[Duke of Caxias]] (1803-1880)\n* [[Count of Porto Alegre]] (1804\u20131875)\n* [[Marcos Ant\u00f4nio de Ara\u00fajo, Viscount of Itajub\u00e1|Viscount of Itajub\u00e1]] (1805\u20131884)\n* [[Manuel de Ara\u00fajo Porto-Alegre, Baron of Santo \u00c2ngelo|Baron of Santo \u00c2ngelo]] (1806\u20131879)\n* [[Jos\u00e9 Paranhos, Viscount of Rio Branco|Viscount of Rio Branco]] (1819\u20131880)\n* [[Jo\u00e3o Lustosa da Cunha Paranagu\u00e1, Marquis of Paranagu\u00e1]] (1821\u20131912)\n* [[Jos\u00e9 de Alencar]] (1829\u20131877)\n* [[Ant\u00f4nio Conselheiro]] (1830-1897)\n* [[:pt:Gaspar da Silveira Martins|Gaspar da Silveira Martins]] (1835-1901)\n* [[Ant\u00f4nio Carlos Gomes|Carlos Gomes]] (1836\u20131896)\n* [[Afonso Celso, Viscount of Ouro Preto]] (1836\u20131912)\n* [[Andr\u00e9 Rebou\u00e7as]] (1838\u20131898)\n* [[Machado de Assis]] (1839\u20131908)\n* [[Joaquim Nabuco]] (1839\u20131910)\n* [[Viscount of Taunay]] (1843-1899)\n* [[Baron of Rio Branco]] (1845\u20131912)\n* [[Jos\u00e9 do Patroc\u00ednio]] (1853-1905)\n* [[Alberto Santos-Dumont]] (1873\u20131932)\n* [[Monteiro Lobato]] (1882\u20131948)\n* [[C\u00e2mara Cascudo]] (1898-1986)\n* [[Plinio Corr\u00eaa de Oliveira]] (1908-1995)\n* [[Jos\u00e9 Osvaldo de Meira Penna]] (1917\u20132017)\n* [[Ariano Suassuna]] (1927\u20132014)\n* [[Prince Bertrand of Orl\u00e9ans-Braganza]] (born 1941)<ref name=TheNoite>{{cite web|url =http://www.sbt.com.br/thenoite/fiquepordentro/97102/Danilo-Gentili-recebe-o-principe-Dom-Bertrand-no-The-Noite.html|title = Danilo Gentili recebe o Pr\u00edncipe Dom Bertrand no The Noite|publisher=SBT|date=2017-09-22 |accessdate=2017-11-18}}</ref>\n* [[Olavo de Carvalho]] (born 1947)<ref name=\"BBC April 2019\"/