rdon ||\n|-\n|2014\n|''[[Welcome to Me]]''|| Rich Ruskin ||\n|-\n|2014\n|''[[X-Men: Days of Future Past]]''|| Scott Summers / Cyclops || Cameo\n|-\n|2015\n|''[[Accidental Love]]''|| Scott ||\n|-\n| 2015 || data-sort-value=\"D Train, The\" |''[[The D Train]]''|| Oliver Lawless || \n|-\n|2015\n| ''[[Into the Grizzly Maze]]'' || Rowan ||\n|-\n|2015\n| ''[[Unfinished Business (2015 film)|Unfinished Business]]'' || Jim Spinch ||\n|-\n| 2017 || data-sort-value=\"Female Brain, The\" | ''[[The Female Brain (film)|The Female Brain]]'' || Adam Simmons ||\n|-\n|2017\n| ''[[Shock and Awe (film)|Shock and Awe]]'' || Warren Strobel ||\n|-\n| 2018 || ''[[Henchmen (film)|Henchmen]]'' || Hank (voice) || \n|-\n| 2019 || ''[[Once Upon a Time in Hollywood]]'' || [[Burt Reynolds]] || Extended cut\n|-\n| 2020 || ''[[Sonic the Hedgehog (film)|Sonic the Hedgehog]]'' || Tom Wachowski || \n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year !! Title !! Role !! class=\"unsortable\" |Notes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |1993\n|''[[In the Line of Duty: Ambush in Waco]]''|| Steven Willis || Television film\n|-\n|''[[Joe's Life]]''|| Brian || Episode: \"Parental Guidance Not Suggested?\"\n|-\n|''[[The Nanny]]''|| Eddie || 2 episodes\n|-\n| ''[[Saved by the Bell: The New Class]]'' || Chad Westerfield || Episode: \"Homecoming King\"\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |1994\n|''[[Boogies Diner]]''|| Jason || Episode #2.28\n|-\n|''Heavenly Road''|| Jeremy || |Television film\n|-\n|''Search and Rescue''|| Television film\n|\n|-\n| rowspan = \"3\" | 1995 || ''[[Blossom]]'' || Josh || Episode: \"The Date\"\n|-\n| ''[[Party of Five]]'' || Griffin Holbrook || Episode: \"The Ides of March\"\n|-\n| ''[[Touched by an Angel]]'' || Jake || Episode: \"Angels on the Air\"\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |1996\n|''Gone in a Heartbeat''|| Michael Galler\n|Television film\n|-\n|''919 Fifth Avenue''|| Will || Television film\n|-\n| 1996\u20131997 ||''[[Second Noah]]'' || Ricky Beckett || 21 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |1997\n|''[[Bella Mafia]]''|| Luka\n|Television film\n|-\n|''[[On the Edge of Innocence]]''|| Jake Walker || Television film\n|-\n| 2001\u20132002 ||''[[Ally McBeal]]'' || Glenn Foy || Main cast (season 5)\n|-\n| 2009 || ''[[Robot Chicken]]'' || [[Jason Chambers]] / Lion (voices) || Episode: \"Especially the Animal Keith Crofford\"\n|-\n| 2011 || ''[[Modern Family]]'' || Barry || Episode: \"[[Slow Down Your Neighbors]]\"\n|-\n| 2012\u20132013 ||''[[30 Rock]]'' || Criss Chros || 13 episodes\n|-\n| 2014\u20132016 ||''[[Wander Over Yonder]]'' || Sir Brad Starlight (voice) || 3 episodes\n|-\n| 2016\u20132018 ||''[[Westworld (TV series)|Westworld]]'' || Teddy Flood || Main cast\n|-\n| 2017 || ''[[Tour de Pharmacy]]'' || Rex Honeycut || Television film\n|-\n| 2019 || ''[[Dead to Me (TV series)|Dead to Me]]'' || Steve Wood || Main cast\n|-\n| rowspan = \"2\" | 2020 || ''[[Mrs. America (miniseries)|Mrs. America]]'' || Phil Crane || Upcoming series\n|-\n| ''[[The Stand (upcoming miniseries)|The Stand]]'' || Stu Redman\n|Upcoming series\n|}\n\n===Music videos===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Artist(s)\n! Role\n! scope=\"col\"| {{abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n| 1998\n| \"[[Got You (Where I Want You)]]\"\n| [[The Flys (American band)|The Flys]]\n| {{N/A|None}}\n|\n|-\n| 2020\n| \"[[Imagine (John Lennon song)|Imagine (Stand for Corona)]]\"\n| Artists for We Are One  \n| Himself\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/03/19/celebrities/gal-gadot-celebrities-imagine-coronavirus-scli-intl/index.html|title=\nGal Gadot enlists celebrity help for coronavirus 'Imagine' video|work=[[CNN]]|author=Laura Smith-Spark|date=March 19, 2020|accessdate=March 20, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!Year\n!Award\n!Category\n!Nominated work\n!Result\n! class=\"unsortable\" | {{abbr|Ref.|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n|2001\n|[[Blockbuster Entertainment Awards]]\n|Favorite Supporting Actor \u2013 Science Fiction\n|''[[X-Men (film)|X-Men]]''